com.github.dakusui.actionunit.actions

Interface With<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - A type of variable through which this action interacts with another.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Action, Formattable

    public interface With<V>
extends Action

    An interface to access a context variable safely. An instance of this interface corresponds to single context variable.

    See Also:
    Context
